    <section>
      <title>EclipseContent-specific command line tool options</title>
      <p>The "eclipsecontent" transform
      type produces normalized DITA files, along with Eclipse TOC and project files.</p>
      <table>
        <title>EclipseContent options</title>
        <tgroup cols="2">
          <thead>
            <row>
              <entry>Argument</entry>
              <entry>Description</entry>
            </row>
          </thead>
